---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="FAQs" description="Frequently asked questions about therapy with Esther K. Shin, LMFT — insurance, pricing, session format, location, and how to begin.">
  <section class="section text-center" style="padding-top: 3rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ Items -->
  <section class="section" style="padding-top: 0;">
    <div class="container" style="max-width: 680px;">

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-q">Do you accept insurance?</h3>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p>I deeply value your privacy and autonomy. For that reason, I work independently.</p>
          <p>I do offer a monthly superbill, which is available upon request.</p>
          <p>PPO insurance plans will often accept superbills from out-of-network private practice therapists and allow you to receive partial compensation for session fees. You would be responsible for submitting these superbills to your insurance company.</p>
          <p>It may be helpful for you to reach out to your insurance company first to determine how much they can reimburse you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-q">How much does therapy cost?</h3>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p>Therapy is a financial, time, and emotional investment in you.</p>
          <ul class="faq-pricing">
            <li><strong>Individual Sessions</strong> (45–50 minutes): <strong>$200</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Couples Sessions</strong> (50–60 minutes): <strong>$215</strong></li>
            <li><strong>Family Sessions</strong> (50–60 minutes): <strong>$215</strong></li>
          </ul>
          <p>I offer a limited number of sliding scale spots based on need, and I provide reduced fees for multiple times a week therapy.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-q">How do you accept payment?</h3>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p>Session can be paid by debit, credit, FSA, or HSA cards. I also accept payments via Zelle.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-q">What is your cancellation policy?</h3>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p>I ask for at least 48 hours of cancellation notice prior to our scheduled session by means of email or voicemail. If I do not receive adequate notice, the full session fee will be charged.</p>
          <p>However, there will be no late cancellation charge if we are able to reschedule within the same session period.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-q">What is the first session like?</h3>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p>Prior to the initial session, I will send you a link to set up your client portal. Here you can access and fill out paperwork for us to begin our work together.</p>
          <p>At your session, we will review questions you had about the paperwork, spend time getting to know you, address what brings you into therapy, and set up goals for treatment.</p>
          <p>The first several sessions allow me to get a sense of what has been going on for you and what we will be addressing in treatment.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-q">What is the length and frequency of therapy? How long will I be in therapy?</h3>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p>Sessions are typically 45 minutes for individuals and 50 minutes for couples and families. I have found therapy works best weekly for most people. Consistent sessions are key to building a good rapport, progress/growth, and a secure safe space.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-q">Where do we meet for session?</h3>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p><strong>In-person:</strong> My office is located at <strong>1370 N. Brea Blvd, Suite 234, Fullerton, CA 92835</strong> at the Hillcrest Office Park. Upon your arrival, please use your phone to scan the QR code that is hanging in the lobby to check-in.</p>
          <p><strong>Online / Teletherapy:</strong> You will receive an email with a link to our session and I will join you at the scheduled time.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-q">Do you offer online sessions / teletherapy?</h3>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p>I offer HIPAA-compliant telehealth sessions through SimplePractice so that you can participate from the comforts of your own home. You will receive an email with a link prior to each session to access our scheduled time.</p>
          <p><strong>For telehealth sessions please remember to:</strong></p>
          <ul>
            <li>Have a secure WIFI signal</li>
            <li>Be in a private location so that there are no unwanted interruptions</li>
            <li>Use your headphones if needed</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-q">Is your office ADA-compliant?</h3>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p>There is an ADA-compliant ramp (northeast end of the building) from the parking lot to the courtyard as well as a large elevator to reach my second-floor office. If you need any assistance, please do not hesitate to reach out.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item">
        <h3 class="faq-q">Still have questions?</h3>
        <div class="faq-a">
          <p>Feel free to reach out with any other questions via email or voicemail. I will get back to you as soon as possible.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- How to begin CTA -->
  <section class="section section-alt text-center">
    <div class="container">
      <h2>How do I begin my therapy journey?</h2>
      <p style="max-width: 560px; margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;">
        Schedule a free 15-minute phone consultation. We can briefly discuss what's bringing you into therapy in this season, answer questions you may have, address the fee, and see if we will be a good fit.
      </p>
      <a href="/contact/" class="btn">Reach out</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .faq-item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    padding: 1.5rem 0;
  }
  .faq-item:last-of-type {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
  .faq-q {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    cursor: default;
  }
  .faq-a p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
  }
  .faq-a ul {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }
  .faq-a li {
    margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
  }
  .faq-pricing {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin: 1rem 0;
  }
  .faq-pricing li {
    padding: 0.4rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border-light);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }
  .faq-pricing li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }
</style>
